Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) - The paper deals with image fusion techniques which is a subfield of computer vision. 
2. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) - The paper discusses various analytical techniques for evaluating the quality of image fusion which can be related to information retrieval. 
3. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with techniques for combining multiple images into a single image which can be considered as a multimedia application. 
4. cs.GR (Graphics) - The paper deals with image processing techniques which can be related to graphics. 
5. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper discusses various statistical techniques for image fusion which can be related to data structures and algorithms.
